---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="First Crack 서비스 이용약관 — 서비스 이용 규칙, 책임, 결제 및 환불 정책." />
    <title>Terms of Service — First Crack</title>
  </head>
  <body>

    <!-- NAV -->
    <header class="nav">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
          <span class="nav-logo-text">First Crack</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Main menu">
          <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
          <a href="/login" class="nav-link">Log in</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="legal-page">
      <div class="container container-narrow">
        <div class="legal-meta">
          <div>
            <h1 class="legal-title">Terms of Service</h1>
            <p class="legal-date">Last updated: July 9, 2026</p>
          </div>
          <p class="legal-url"><span class="legal-url-label">Service</span> firstcrackiscoming.com</p>
        </div>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing or using First Crack ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use the Service. We reserve the right to update these terms; continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p>First Crack provides a cloud-based platform for coffee roasting profile management, live roast monitoring, and quality analytics. The Service includes a desktop application, web dashboard, and associated APIs.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">3. Accounts & Registration</h2>
          <ul class="legal-ul">
            <li>You must be at least 16 years old to use the Service.</li>
            <li>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials.</li>
            <li>You must provide accurate, current registration information.</li>
            <li>You may not share your account with unauthorized users.</li>
            <li>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">4. Subscriptions & Payments</h2>
          <ul class="legal-ul">
            <li><strong>Free tier:</strong> Limited to 20 batches per month with basic features.</li>
            <li><strong>Paid plans:</strong> Billed monthly or annually as selected at checkout. Prices are in USD.</li>
            <li><strong>Cancellation:</strong> You may cancel at any time. Access continues until the end of the current billing period.</li>
            <li><strong>Refunds:</strong> No refunds for partial billing periods. If you cancel mid-cycle, you retain access until the next billing date.</li>
            <li><strong>Price changes:</strong> We will notify you 30 days before any price change. Continued use after the change constitutes acceptance.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">5. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p>You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="legal-ul">
            <li>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws.</li>
            <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, decompile, or extract the source code of the desktop application.</li>
            <li>Upload malicious code, viruses, or anything that disrupts the Service.</li>
            <li>Interfere with other users' access to the Service.</li>
            <li>Use automated bots or scrapers without our written permission.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">6. Data Ownership</h2>
          <ul class="legal-ul">
            <li><strong>Your data:</strong> You retain full ownership of all roast profiles, batch notes, and other data you upload to First Crack.</li>
            <li><strong>License to us:</strong> You grant First Crack a limited license to store, process, and display your data solely to provide the Service to you.</li>
            <li><strong>Anonymized data:</strong> We may use anonymized, aggregated data for platform improvement and benchmarking. This data cannot identify you or your roastery.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>First Crack is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. We are not liable for:</p>
          <ul class="legal-ul">
            <li>Loss of roast data due to user error or failure to back up.</li>
            <li>Decisions made based on platform analytics — roasting decisions remain the responsibility of the user.</li>
            <li>Downtime or service interruptions beyond reasonable efforts to maintain uptime.</li>
            <li>Indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of the Service.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">8. Termination</h2>
          <p>We may terminate or suspend your account immediately if you materially breach these terms. Upon termination:</p>
          <ul class="legal-ul">
            <li>Your access to the Service ceases.</li>
            <li>We will provide a 30-day window to export your data before permanent deletion.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the Republic of Korea. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Seoul, South Korea.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2 class="legal-h2">10. Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about these terms, please contact <a href="mailto:hello@firstcrack.io" class="legal-link">hello@firstcrack.io</a>.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <span class="footer-logo">First Crack</span>
          <span class="footer-copy">© 2026</span>
        </div>
        <nav class="footer-links" aria-label="Footer menu">
          <a href="/privacy" class="footer-link">Privacy</a>
          <a href="/terms" class="footer-link">Terms</a>
          <a href="/docs" class="footer-link">Docs</a>
          <a href="mailto:hello@firstcrack.io" class="footer-link">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>

<style>
  /* ── Legal page layout ── */
  .legal-page {
    padding-block: var(--space-80);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    min-height: calc(100vh - 56px - 80px);
  }
  .legal-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    color: var(--color-fg);
  }
  .legal-date {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-fg-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-48);
  }
  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-40);
  }
  .legal-h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-card);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
    color: var(--color-fg);
  }
  .legal-section p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }
  .legal-ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-16) 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }
  .legal-ul li {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    padding-left: var(--space-20);
    position: relative;
  }
  .legal-ul li::before {
    content: "—";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-mint);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .legal-link {
    color: var(--color-fg);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-mint);
    transition: opacity var(--motion-fast) ease;
  }
  .legal-link:hover {
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* ── Service URL header ── */
  .legal-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-24);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-48);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .legal-url {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-standard);
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-16);
    white-space: nowrap;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }
  .legal-url-label {
    font-size: var(--text-micro);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-fg-muted);
  }

  /* ── Nav (same as index) ── */
  .nav {
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-fg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .nav-logo-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-nav);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-24);
    height: 56px;
  }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }
  .nav .nav-link {
    color: var(--color-fg-secondary);
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-subtle);
    transition: color var(--motion-fast) ease;
    font-size: var(--text-nav);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav .nav-link:hover { color: var(--color-fg); }
  .nav-logo { text-decoration: none; color: var(--color-fg); }

  /* ── Footer (same as index) ── */
  .site-footer {
    background: var(--color-dark);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    padding-block: var(--space-32);
  }
  .footer-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .footer-brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-12);
  }
  .footer-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-nav);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }
  .footer-copy {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }
  .footer-links { display: flex; gap: var(--space-24); }
  .footer-link {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    transition: color var(--motion-fast) ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .footer-link:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-20); }
    .legal-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }
  }
</style>
